    "Likewise, the fraud detection system detecting \"sham marriages\" in the UK primarily flags cases requiring further investigation.",
    "At the same time, the risk assessment will be \"available to the caseworker if an application for permanent residence is submitted and is considered as part of that decision,\" hence it is usable in evidence.",
